<i>adverb</i>: 따따부따 [따따부따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>따따부따 [따따부따]</dt><br>
<dd>criticizingly; vociferously</dd><br>
<dd>무슨 일에 괜히 참견하여 시끄럽게 떠들며 무뚝뚝한 말씨로 따지는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound or describing the act of someone criticizing bluntly and noisily while meddling in another's affair.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>